Class Pair<T,K>

java.lang.Object
utils.Pair<T,K>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the first value
K - the type of the second value
public class Pair<T,K> extends Object
A generic class representing a pair of values.

This class can be used to store and manipulate a pair of related values of any types.
